column5: Official Announcement:  The Government of Canada today announced that it is changing its emblem from a Maple Leaf to a CONDOM because it more accurately reflects the government's political stance. A condom allows for inflation, halts production, destroys the next generation, protects a bunch of pricks, and gives you a sense of security while you're actually being screwed.  Damn, it just doesn't get more accurate than that!
Maybe the Toronto Maple Leafs should consider changing to that to. LMAO.
